an elementary school vice-principal.

90
00:08:00,521 --> 00:08:03,316
I see. They're both educators.

91
00:08:04,192 --> 00:08:05,443
Then what about you?

92
00:08:05,526 --> 00:08:07,528
Which university did you go to?

93
00:08:07,612 --> 00:08:09,614
