97
00:08:19,665 --> 00:08:20,833
It's mine.

98
00:08:20,917 --> 00:08:23,294
I did take out a loan,

99
00:08:23,377 --> 00:08:26,088
but it's registered under my name.

100
00:08:26,964 --> 00:08:32,136
