136
00:10:09,483 --> 00:10:11,569
I thought your feelings were genuine.

137
00:10:11,652 --> 00:10:12,945
They are.

138
00:10:13,029 --> 00:10:15,781
-But you don't want to get married.
-That's true too!

139
00:10:15,865 --> 00:10:17,033
How does that…

140
00:10:18,034 --> 00:10:19,368
Unbelievable.

141
